title: 19 Kids and Counting - s00e14 - A Decade of Duggar Delivaries
description:
Let's try to keep comments about the torrent, and not about recent news stories.

 Before they aired the episode about Jill's baby, TLC aired a three hour long special that covered every single birth since Jackson. As this episode features clips from over 11 years, video quality varies greatly from the earlier episodes (filmed in 16x9 SD) to the newer episodes.

 As this was a special, and not an episode, according to TheTVD, this would make it a season 0 episode. Feel free to rename it.
